67
00:05:01,892 --> 00:05:03,052
That's right.

68
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,525
Because he resembles me...

69
00:05:07,865 --> 00:05:09,730
Because he has gone through life

70
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:12,325
