83
00:06:21,305 --> 00:06:23,432
<i>No matter what, I will...</i>

84
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:28,705
<i>protect you!</i>

85
00:06:38,055 --> 00:06:40,046
Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!

86
