a long time!

88
00:06:58,108 --> 00:07:01,839
The spiraling series of Naruto Uzumaki's
Ninja Handbook starts now!

89
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:05,810
W-What's up with this...
large number of clones?!

90
00:07:06,383 --> 00:07:07,816
