To get Gaara in that state...

112
00:08:53,857 --> 00:08:56,849
<i>Where does that strength come from?</i>

113
00:08:57,795 --> 00:09:01,697
<i>No way!</i>
<i>There's no way...</i>

114
00:09:04,034 --> 00:09:09,131
No way I'll... lose to... a guy like this!

115
00:09:21,351 --> 00:09:23,216
W-What's... that?

116
00:09:30,694 --> 00:09:33,060
<i>It finally...emerged.</i>

117
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,177
<i>The Perfect Possession!</i>

118
00:09:55,719 --> 00:09:59,951
