the monster inside that guy.

119
00:10:00,758 --> 00:10:06,287
I didn't think you would
expose this form!

120
00:10:11,635 --> 00:10:12,533
Naruto!

121
00:10:15,072 --> 00:10:17,040
Darn... my body!

122
00:10:19,042 --> 00:10:22,307
<i>My Chakra has...</i>
<i>with all those clones earlier on...</i>

123
00:10:28,418 --> 00:10:29,146
<i>Sakura!</i>

124
00:10:30,087 --> 00:10:31,577
D-Darn!

125
00:10:37,961 --> 00:10:42,261
I, Inu, Tori, Saru, Hitsuji...

126
00:10:42,499 --> 00:10:44,433
This will mark your end...

127
00:10:45,135 --> 00:10:47,569
- Sand Burial!
- Summoning Jutsu!

128
00:10:55,646 --> 00:10:58,376
It's amazing that he can utilize
a Summoning Jutsu in that state...

129
00:11:00,551 --> 00:11:01,779
I will protect...

130
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,844
Sakura!

131
00:11:17,434 --> 00:11:19,800
Naruto Uzumaki...

132
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:27,401
You continue to give me
such pleasure...

133
00:11:27,878 --> 00:11:31,974
<i>Naruto...</i>
<i>What in the...world...?</i>

134
00:11:32,816 --> 00:11:35,717
<i>My hours of practice</i>
<i>are finally paying off!</i>

135
00:11:36,186 --> 00:11:38,211
<i>I can do it!</i>

136
00:11:38,655 --> 00:11:40,623
- What is this?
- Huh?

137
00:11:41,124 --> 00:11:44,423
Not you again!
What in the world do you want?

138
00:11:45,462 --> 00:11:46,360
Huh?!

139
00:11:50,901 --> 00:11:55,099
<i>That must be...</i>
<i>the Shukaku of the Sand.</i>

140
00:11:55,873 --> 00:11:59,468
Chief Toad!
Come join me in this fight!

141
00:12:03,914 --> 00:12:04,903
No way!

142
00:12:05,015 --> 00:12:06,141
What?!

143
00:12:06,850 --> 00:12:10,342
Why would I go out of my way
and fight a guy like that?

144
00:12:10,888 --> 00:12:12,549
That's idiotic!

145
00:12:12,623 --> 00:12:13,954
Why?!

146
00:12:14,091 --> 00:12:17,026
You told me the other day that you
would make me your henchman!

147
00:12:17,294 --> 00:12:20,457
It's only natural for a chief
to help out his henchman!

148
00:12:20,797 --> 00:12:22,594
That's respect and duty, right?!

149
00:12:23,267 --> 00:12:26,998
It's true I told you
I'd make you my henchman...

150
00:12:27,838 --> 00:12:32,138
But we haven't even exchanged
cups of <i>sake</i> to seal our relationship yet...

151
00:12:32,209 --> 00:12:35,804
Gimme a break! I'm still underage!

152
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:37,471
I can't drink alcohol!

153
00:12:38,515 --> 00:12:41,951
Don't say that and just listen
to what this guy says, Pop!

154
00:12:42,019 --> 00:12:43,486
Huh?! Pop?!

155
00:12:44,021 --> 00:12:47,855
Why are you here, Gamakichi?

156
00:12:48,225 --> 00:12:50,591
I had lots of time on my hands,
so I came to visit...

157
00:12:51,094 --> 00:12:53,494
Huh? Huh?
You're father and son?

158
00:12:54,064 --> 00:12:56,897
Then that guy over there
tried to bully me!

159
00:12:58,168 --> 00:13:00,033
What was that?!

160
00:13:00,871 --> 00:13:03,999
When that happened,
this guy here rescued me...

161
00:13:04,374 --> 00:13:06,569
He clashed with that monster...

162
00:13:06,643 --> 00:13:09,441
Pretty interesting guy.

163
00:13:11,748 --> 00:13:13,113
I see...

164
00:13:20,824 --> 00:13:25,124
Kid... I recognize you
as my henchman...

165
00:13:26,063 --> 00:13:30,762
and I'll show you what duty
and respect means!

166
00:13:46,016 --> 00:13:52,888
I'll make you pay the price
good and proper, you underling!

167
00:13:57,127 --> 00:13:59,357
Hang on tight!

168
00:14:06,003 --> 00:14:08,437
How's that?!

169
00:14:15,012 --> 00:14:16,138
<i>Awesome...</i>

170
00:14:38,635 --> 00:14:40,466
<i>What a guy...</i>

171
00:14:40,704 --> 00:14:41,966
<i>He's so heavy,</i>

172
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:44,303
<i>I could barely manage to</i>
<i>thrust my dagger through him.</i>

173
00:14:45,042 --> 00:14:46,669
<i>If I don't hurry up,</i>

174
00:14:46,743 --> 00:14:48,973
<i>this battle will change</i>
<i>the shape of the landscape.</i>

175
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:51,476
Hey! Hey! Chief!

176
00:14:51,615 --> 00:14:54,812
Sakura is over that way,
so don't move that way!

177
00:14:54,918 --> 00:14:57,216
Please lure him in this direction.

178
00:14:57,754 --> 00:14:59,415
Sakura...?

179
00:14:59,890 --> 00:15:02,484
That's his girlfriend, Pop.

180
00:15:02,993 --> 00:15:04,620
I've got to take that guy down.

181
00:15:05,195 --> 00:15:07,186
Otherwise, I won't be able
to rescue Sakura!

182
00:15:10,634 --> 00:15:12,124
Interesting!

183
00:15:12,836 --> 00:15:16,795
This is interesting
Naruto Uzumaki!

184
00:15:16,973 --> 00:15:18,133
<i>T-This isn't good!</i>

185
00:15:18,909 --> 00:15:21,241
<i>That Gaara...</i>
<i>He's intending to do that thing.</i>

186
00:15:21,611 --> 00:15:22,942
<i>I better get out of here!</i>

187
00:15:37,260 --> 00:15:39,626
Huh? That is...

188
00:15:41,098 --> 00:15:44,363
That's... the medium...?

189
00:15:45,435 --> 00:15:48,598
To thank you for entertaining me
up to now...

190
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:53,432
I'll show you the real power...

191
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:55,444
of the Sand Spirit!

192
00:15:56,713 --> 00:15:58,374
The circles under his eyes...

193
00:15:59,616 --> 00:16:02,517
Those are symptoms of
insomnia which indicate

194
00:16:02,586 --> 00:16:06,113
that the medium is also possessed
by the Shukaku of the Sand.

195
00:16:07,491 --> 00:16:08,480
Insomnia...?

196
00:16:10,594 --> 00:16:13,722
Those who are possessed
by the Demon Raccoon Shukaku

197
00:16:13,930 --> 00:16:18,264
are unable to sleep soundly
through the entire night.

198
00:16:18,869 --> 00:16:20,598
Because of the terror...

199
00:16:22,172 --> 00:16:28,077
If one sleeps, Shukaku will slowly
eat away at their personality

200
00:16:28,278 --> 00:16:32,078
and eventually that person
is no longer himself.

201
00:16:35,852 --> 00:16:38,514
Because he normally
doesn't get much sleep...

202
00:16:38,588 --> 00:16:44,049
the medium's personality
tends to... become unstable.

203
00:16:45,495 --> 00:16:46,223
Oh...

204
00:16:48,331 --> 00:16:52,461
Therefore, usually while
the medium is awake,

205
00:16:52,669 --> 00:16:56,537
the power of Shukaku is
normally controlled.

206
00:16:57,407 --> 00:16:58,874
However...

207
00:17:00,944 --> 00:17:04,903
when that medium sleeps...

208
00:17:05,148 --> 00:17:06,513
Playing Possum Jutsu!

209
00:17:18,862 --> 00:17:20,295
He's done it...!

210
00:17:21,665 --> 00:17:24,532
W-What's gonna happen, Chief?

211
00:17:25,735 --> 00:17:29,171
If one sets Playing Possum Jutsu
into motion...

212
00:17:29,272 --> 00:17:31,604
...the Shukaku will appear!

213
00:17:38,181 --> 00:17:42,311
I'm finally able to emerge!

214
00:17:44,254 --> 00:17:46,188
That's the Shukaku?

215
00:17:47,090 --> 00:17:48,614
He's pretty funky...

216
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:55,720
Right away!
The guy I wanna kill! You!

217
00:17:57,067 --> 00:17:58,091
I'm gonna jump...

218
00:17:58,468 --> 00:17:58,991
Huh?

219
00:17:59,302 --> 00:18:02,362
Wind Style: Air Bullets!

220
00:18:05,208 --> 00:18:07,642
Water Style: Water Bullets!

221
00:18:16,753 --> 00:18:19,415
That's practically a storm...

222
00:18:20,190 --> 00:18:22,454
What kind of a battle is this...?!

223
00:18:26,162 --> 00:18:28,130
Chief! I told you,
not in that direction!

224
00:18:28,265 --> 00:18:31,166
Shut up! I know!

225
00:18:32,836 --> 00:18:34,303
Air Bullets!

226
00:18:35,305 --> 00:18:36,499
Water Bullets!

227
00:18:40,210 --> 00:18:41,507
Too bad...

228
00:18:41,811 --> 00:18:43,711
This isn't good, Chief!
There's one shot left...!

229
00:18:52,756 --> 00:18:54,656
Yeah! I killed it...

230
00:18:54,724 --> 00:18:56,351
I killed it!

231
00:19:00,297 --> 00:19:02,527
That hurts...!

232
00:19:03,099 --> 00:19:04,623
How dare you shoot me

233
00:19:04,701 --> 00:19:07,033
with bullets containing
stupid amounts of Chakra!

234
00:19:08,004 --> 00:19:11,633
Even I can't take that many shots!

235
00:19:11,775 --> 00:19:13,504
What should we do?!

236
00:19:13,810 --> 00:19:18,713
For a start,
wake up that medium kid!

237
00:19:19,215 --> 00:19:20,443
It will release that Jutsu!

238
00:19:20,517 --> 00:19:22,109
How do we go about waking him?!

239
00:19:22,185 --> 00:19:25,120
Give him a good punch!

240
00:19:26,956 --> 00:19:28,253
Water Bullets!

241
00:19:28,925 --> 00:19:30,586
Like I'll take that!

242
00:19:34,664 --> 00:19:35,426
Now!

243
00:19:42,806 --> 00:19:46,674
Chief, I can't hit him
unless you hold him down!

244
00:19:48,211 --> 00:19:53,444
This Toad doesn't have fangs or claws
to hold that guy's movement.

245
00:19:53,850 --> 00:19:56,182
What should we do then?!

246
00:19:56,419 --> 00:20:00,515
We'll use the Transform Jutsu to
change into something that has those!

247
00:20:02,559 --> 00:20:03,617
But with that said...

248
00:20:03,693 --> 00:20:06,560
I'm not particularly good
at transformations.

249
00:20:06,629 --> 00:20:07,288
Huh?

250
00:20:07,530 --> 00:20:12,490
So you will act as my will
and make the Sign!

251
00:20:12,569 --> 00:20:13,797
Whaaaat?!

252
00:20:13,870 --> 00:20:15,701
Time for a combined transformation!

253
00:20:15,872 --> 00:20:17,203
Uh... Okay!

254
00:20:17,907 --> 00:20:20,637
We got to have fangs and claws!

255
00:20:20,910 --> 00:20:22,400
Umm...

256
00:20:22,812 --> 00:20:24,609
Let's go

257
00:20:25,515 --> 00:20:27,881
Wait...
Say, w wait a second...!

258
00:20:28,918 --> 00:20:31,386
F-Fangs and claws... Fangs and claws...
Fangs and claws!

259
00:20:33,189 --> 00:20:35,521
Transform!

260
00:20:41,598 --> 00:20:43,088
Transform Jutsu!

261
00:20:50,373 --> 00:20:51,203
That's the...!

262
00:21:09,393 --> 00:21:13,193
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

263
00:21:14,331 --> 00:21:18,165
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

264
00:21:19,703 --> 00:21:27,576
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

265
00:21:28,545 --> 00:21:30,513
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

266
00:21:33,450 --> 00:21:36,317
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

267
00:21:36,853 --> 00:21:41,950
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

268
00:21:42,025 --> 00:21:47,554
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

269
00:21:47,664 --> 00:21:52,465
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

270
00:21:52,536 --> 00:21:57,439
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

271
00:21:57,507 --> 00:22:06,677
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

272
00:22:07,150 --> 00:22:12,486
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

273
00:22:12,556 --> 00:22:17,926
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

274
00:22:19,796 --> 00:22:29,728
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

275
00:22:37,414 --> 00:22:41,475
I don't know about your past,
and my past doesn't matter either!

276
00:22:41,985 --> 00:22:44,920
I only have people who I must protect.

277
00:22:45,555 --> 00:22:46,647
Hey you with no eyebrows!

278
00:22:46,890 --> 00:22:50,257
Let's just end this as similar fighters.

279
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:52,457
I will finish this with my next hit.

280
00:22:52,829 --> 00:22:57,493
This will be, absolutely and totally,
the last one!

281
00:22:58,301 --> 00:23:01,896
Next time:
"Beyond the Limit of Darkness and Light"
